<h4 id="triggerparametersresponse">Trigger<wbr>Parameters<wbr>Response</h4>



<div>
<pulumi-choosable type="language" values="csharp">
<dl class="resources-properties"><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="endby_csharp">
<a data-swiftype-name="resource-property" data-swiftype-type="text" href="#endby_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">End<wbr>By</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">string</span>
